      <title>南非领导人敦促在特朗普改组中G-20合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/south-african-leader-urges-g-20-cooperation-amid-trump-shakeup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨（Cyril Ramaphosa）呼吁在20个国家组织中加强合作，因为他的美国对手唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）为追求他的美国第一议程而颠覆了世界秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/south-african-leader-urges-g-20-cooperation-amid-trump-shakeup</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 07:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当G-20财务部长见面时，开普敦与山区大火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/cape-town-battles-mountain-fires-as-g-20-finance-ministers-meet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消防员扑灭了一场大火，周三席卷了开普敦的地标山山，这是20个国家的财务部长和中央银行州长开始在该市开会的，这吞没了开普敦的地标山山。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/cape-town-battles-mountain-fires-as-g-20-finance-ministers-meet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 06:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国希望我们在乌克兰停火后提供备份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/france-expects-us-to-provide-backup-after-ukraine-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长埃里克·伦巴德（Eric Lombard）表示，他希望美国在乌克兰和俄罗斯之间达成停火后，为欧洲部队提供备份，以帮助维持和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/france-expects-us-to-provide-backup-after-ukraine-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 05:45:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和伊拉克谈论“快速”恢复关键的石油管道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/us-and-iraq-talk-about-quickly-resuming-key-oil-pipeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和伊拉克讨论了一条重大的管道，该管道可以将石油从中东国家运送到全球市场，此前几乎两年前在区域成本纠纷之后，该链接被关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/us-and-iraq-talk-about-quickly-resuming-key-oil-pipeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 05:15:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税动荡在G-20会议上蒙上了阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/g-20-convene-in-south-africa-as-trump-tariffs-spark-discord</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长和中央银行俱乐部，他们在四分之一世纪的市场崩溃，衰退，战争和大流行会议上引导了全球经济，本周面临新的逆风，以实现更广泛的繁荣＆Mdash的目标。关税和贸易战的迫在眉睫的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/g-20-convene-in-south-africa-as-trump-tariffs-spark-discord</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟向努力竞争的行业推销新的干净交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/eu-to-pitch-new-clean-deal-to-industries-struggling-to-compete</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲联盟将推出一项计划，以提高集团的竞争力，因为其行业努力平衡雄心勃勃的气候目标并增加了美国和中国的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/eu-to-pitch-new-clean-deal-to-industries-struggling-to-compete</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的前CDC负责人将马斯克的总督削减为“反科学”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/china-s-ex-cdc-chief-slams-musk-s-doge-cuts-as-anti-science</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的特别顾问削减了研究预算之后，中国疾病预防控制中心（CDC）的前负责人指责埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）损害了科学，这是他削减联邦支出的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/china-s-ex-cdc-chief-slams-musk-s-doge-cuts-as-anti-science</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 04:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国威胁迫使加拿大自由主义者促进军事目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/us-threats-mean-canada-must-strengthen-military-candidates-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据竞争者称，加拿大必须迅速提高其国防支出，以达到北约目标，同时也将自己脱离美国制造的军事装备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/us-threats-mean-canada-must-strengthen-military-candidates-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 03:32:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁要将斯塔默推向更全球的军事议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/trump-s-threats-push-starmer-into-a-more-global-military-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）席卷了承诺提高生活水平并发展英国经济的权力。但是现在，他的英超联盟以紧急且完全不同的重点：在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）上推动的世界秩序中，保存欧洲安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/trump-s-threats-push-starmer-into-a-more-global-military-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 19:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟寻求印度对俄罗斯制裁的帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/eu-to-seek-india-s-help-to-enforce-sanctions-on-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席厄休拉·冯·德莱恩（Ursula von der Leyen）将在本周两位领导人本周在新德里开会时，向印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）寻求对俄罗斯制裁的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/eu-to-seek-india-s-help-to-enforce-sanctions-on-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 15:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
